
Given a string s and a dictionary of words dict, determine if s can be segmented into a space-separated sequence of one or more dictionary words.

For example, given
s = "leetcode",
dict = ["leet", "code"].

Return true because "leetcode" can be segmented as "leet code".

要注意的是，substring（0，1）是第一个字母，而不是两个


public class Solution {
    public boolean wordBreak(String s, Set<String> dict) {
        
       
        
        int [] res = new int [s.length()+1];
        res[0] = 1;这个数组是用来标注一个单词的结束的，下一个检查，必要保证这个是true，也就是一个单词的结束
        
        
        for(int i = 1 ; i < s.length()+1 ; i++ ){注意这里的开头是1，结尾是length+1，总的循环次数还是length的次数
            for(int j = 0; j < i ; j++){
                if(res[j] == 1 && dict.contains(s.substring(j,i))) res[i] = 1;
                if(res[i]==1) break;
            }
        }
        
        
       return res[s.length()]==1?true:false; 
    }
}
